Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.38,0:22:45.85,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}摩擦を知らない優しさで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.98,0:22:48.80,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}霧深い森に迷い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.95,0:22:55.95,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}ふたり千年遠ざかる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.57,0:22:58.61,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}灰色のハーモニー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:23:01.02,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}愛と自由は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.19,0:23:03.93,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}なぜ出会うことできない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.14,0:23:09.66,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}いつか荒れ野の露になるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.76,0:23:14.26,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}心の重さ　愛の重さ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.42,0:23:16.87,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}全身で聴いていた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.01,0:23:22.76,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}憂い　気高い　後ろ姿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.50,0:23:31.07,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}あなたの夢を守り抜けたなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.31,0:23:36.66,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}月にあらがう長いフレア
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.85,0:23:44.15,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}始まりもせず終わる物語
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.36,0:23:48.20,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}そっと空に置く涙は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.42,0:23:50.37,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}未完のシンフォニア
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.52,0:23:51.83,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}あなただけに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.93,0:23:53.16,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}君だけに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.33,0:23:58.77,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}星の遺言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.69,0:24:05.78,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}あなたに会いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.38,0:22:45.85,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}不了解摩擦的那份溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.98,0:22:48.80,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}迷茫在大霧彌漫的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.95,0:22:55.95,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}兩人相隔著千年的距離
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.57,0:22:58.61,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}相伴著灰色的調和
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:23:01.02,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}愛和自由
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.19,0:23:03.93,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}卻遲遲無法相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.14,0:23:09.66,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}直到荒野凝結出露水的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.76,0:23:14.26,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}心的重量  愛的重量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.42,0:23:16.87,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}用盡全身的感覺去聆聽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.01,0:23:22.76,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}那憂傷而又高貴的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.50,0:23:31.07,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}如果能夠守護住你的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.31,0:23:36.66,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}伴隨著歲月漫長的流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.85,0:23:44.15,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}沒有開始就已經結束了的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.36,0:23:48.20,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}不經意揮灑在空中的淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.42,0:23:50.37,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}未完成的樂章
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.52,0:23:51.83,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}僅指引你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.93,0:23:53.16,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}只授予你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.33,0:23:58.77,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}繁星的遺言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.69,0:24:05.78,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}想要見到你
